---

<div class="hero">
    <div class="bg">
        <img src="img/bg.webp" alt="Hintergrund" />
    </div>
    <img class="hauke" src="/img/hauke.webp" alt="Hauke Schnau Portrait" />
    <Header />
    <div class="content">
        <div class="subtitle">Hi, ich bin</div>
        <h1>Hauke<br />Schnau.</h1>
        <ul class="features">
            <li>Full-Stack-Entwickler.</li>
            <li>Web Designer.</li>
